pullrequest.title: Use latest version of subt tunnel staging area

content.raw:
I fixed this problem, sort of. I believe there is an issue on the fuel server, where the model download is not updated until someone manually clicks the download button the web-frontend. I'm looking into the underlying problem. 

For this PR, the staging area should work now.
